								<h4>(Program) Paper</h4>
								<input style="width:100%;margin-bottom: 5px;" name="program_paper" data="<%= course_types_subjects_path(format: "json") %>" class="select2-ajax-course-types-subjects multiple" value="" text="" /> 
							</div>-->
						  
